script.name: lib.complexplan.getdata
script.sourceplaintext:
* compute cycle time if $a.time AND $a.time > 0 $longest.time = $a.time else $longest.time = 3600 end
if $a.stations $station = get next key: table=$a.stations key=null while $station gosub sub.GetLongestTime $station = get next key: table=$a.stations key=$station end end if $a.asterods $asteroid = get next key: table=$a.asterods key=null while $asteroid $station = $a.asterods[$asteroid] $obj = $asteroid gosub sub.GetLongestTime $asteroid = get next key: table=$a.asterods key=$asteroid end end if $a.existing $o = get next key: table=$a.existing key=null while $o if $o -> is of class Complex Hub $aFacs = $o ->get factories connected to complex if $aFacs $i = size of array $aFacs while $i dec $i = $obj = $aFacs[$i] $station = $obj -> get ware type code of object gosub sub.GetLongestTime end end else $obj = $o $station = $obj -> get ware type code of object gosub sub.GetLongestTime end $o = get next key: table=$a.existing key=$o end end
$table.products = table alloc $table.resources = table alloc $sub.List = $a.stations gosub sub.GetAllWares
$sub.List = $a.asterods gosub sub.GetAllWares
$sub.List = $a.existing gosub sub.GetAllWares
$table.needed = table alloc $table.surplus = table alloc
if size of table $table.products $ware = get next key: table=$table.products key=null while $ware $ware.needed = $table.resources[$ware] $ware.count = $table.products[$ware] skip if $ware.needed $ware.needed = 0 $ware.remain = $ware.count - $ware.needed if $ware.remain > 0 $table.surplus[$ware] = $ware.remain else if $ware.remain < 0 $tmp = - $ware.remain $table.needed[$ware] = $tmp end $ware = get next key: table=$table.products key=$ware end end
if size of table $table.resources $ware = get next key: table=$table.resources key=null while $ware if not $table.products[$ware] $ware.needed = $table.resources[$ware] $ware.count = 0 $ware.remain = $ware.count - $ware.needed if $ware.remain < 0 $tmp = - $ware.remain $type = get maintype of ware $ware do if $type != [SSTYPE_W_MINERALS] $table.needed[$ware] = $tmp end end $ware = get next key: table=$table.resources key=$ware end end
$ret = create new array, arguments=$longest.time, $table.products, $table.resources, $table.surplus, $table.needed return $ret
sub.GetLongestTime: gosub sub.ComputeEff gosub sub.GetScaleFactor $time = get production time: stationtype=$station, efficiency=$eff, player owned=[TRUE], scale factor=$scale.factor $time = $time * 2 $longest.time = get maximum, $longest.time, $time, null, null, null endsub
sub.GetAllWares: if $sub.List $sub.key = get next key: table=$sub.List key=null while $sub.key $obj = null $asteroid = null $yield = null $station = $sub.key $station.count = $sub.List[$sub.key]
if $sub.key -> exists if $sub.key -> is of class Asteroid $asteroid = $sub.key $yield = $asteroid -> get asteroid yield $station = $sub.List[$sub.key] $station.count = 1 else if $sub.key -> is of class Complex Hub $station.count = 1 $aFacs = $sub.key ->get factories connected to complex if $aFacs $i = size of array $aFacs while $i dec $i = $obj = $aFacs[$i] $station = $obj -> get ware type code of object gosub sub.GetAllWaresFromStation end end $station = null else if $sub.key -> is of class Station $obj = $sub.key $station.count = 1 $station = $sub.key -> get ware type code of object end end do if $station gosub sub.GetAllWaresFromStation $sub.key = get next key: table=$sub.List key=$sub.key end end endsub
sub.GetAllWaresFromStation: gosub sub.ComputeEff $product = get default product: stationtype=$station gosub sub.GetScaleFactor @ $time = [THIS] -> call script lib.complexplan.getproductinfo : Station Type=$station Efficency=$eff IsPlayer=[TRUE] Scale Factor=$scale.factor $prod.count = $time[1] $time = $time[0] $prod.count = $prod.count * $station.count $prod.count = fixed multiply and divide: $prod.count * $longest.time / $time $new.product.count = $table.products[$product] skip if $new.product.count $new.product.count = 0 $new.product.count = $new.product.count + $prod.count $table.products[$product] = $new.product.count
@ $wares = [THIS] -> call script lib.complexplan.getconsumed : Station Type=$station Efficency=$eff Is Player=[TRUE] Scale Factor=$scale.factor Product Amount=null $ware = get next key: table=$wares key=null while $ware $prod.count = $wares[$ware] $prod.count = $prod.count * $station.count $prod.count = fixed multiply and divide: $prod.count * $longest.time / $time $new.product.count = $table.resources[$ware] skip if $new.product.count $new.product.count = 0 $new.product.count = $new.product.count + $prod.count $table.resources[$ware] = $new.product.count $ware = get next key: table=$wares key=$ware end endsub
sub.CountStations: $station.count = 0 $station = get next key: table=$a.stations key=null while $station $amt = $a.stations[$station] $station.count = $amt + $station.count $station = get next key: table=$a.stations key=$station end
$amt = size of table $a.asterods $station.count = $amt + $station.count
if $a.existing $station = get next key: table=$a.existing key=null while $station if $station -> is of class Complex Hub $aFacs = $station ->get factories connected to complex if $aFacs $amt = size of array $aFacs $station.count = $amt + $station.count end else inc $station.count = end $station = get next key: table=$a.existing key=$station end end endsub
sub.ComputeEff: $eff = 26 if $obj -> exists if $obj -> is of class Station $eff = $obj ->get production efficiency endsub end end
$product = get default product: stationtype=$station if is station type a mine: stationtype=$station if $obj -> exists if $obj -> is of class Asteroid $eff = $obj -> get asteroid yield end end else if $product == Energy Cells $energy = $a.sector ->get sun energy factor $eff = fixed multiply: $energy * 8 end endsub
sub.GetScaleFactor: $upgrade.station = null if $upgrades.table if $obj -> exists $upgrade.station = $upgrades.table[$obj] else if is station type a mine: stationtype=$station $upgrade.station = $upgrades.table[$ast] else $upgrade.station = $upgrades.table[$station] end end
if $upgrade.station == 'scale.none' $scale.factor = get station type scale factor: stationtype=$station else if $upgrade.station $scale.factor = $upgrade.lookup.table[$upgrade.station] else if $upgrade.level == 1 $scale.factor = 2 else if $upgrade.level == 2 $scale.factor = 5 else if $upgrade.level == 3 $scale.factor = 10 else if $upgrade.level == 4 $scale.factor = 20 else $scale.factor = 1 end end $val = get station type scale factor: stationtype=$station if $obj -> exists if $obj -> is of class Station $val = $obj ->get station scale factor end end do if $val > $scale.factor $scale.factor = $val endsub
return null
